Package ie.atu.sw

Class EmbeddingsParser

java.lang.Object
ie.atu.sw.EmbeddingsParser
public class EmbeddingsParser extends Object
The EmbeddingsParser class handles parsing word embeddings from a file and storing them in a ConcurrentHashMap for thread-safe operations.
